@startuml
!define ICONS /Users/iworldafric/dev/diagrams/plantuml-stdlib/stdlib/tupadr3
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/bolt.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/brain.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/cog.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/check_circle.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/database.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/sync.puml
!include ICONS/font-awesome-5/microchip.puml
!include ICONS/common.puml

skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #1A5276
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #2980B9
skinparam ActivityFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityFontSize 12
skinparam ActivityArrowColor #5DADE2
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #7D6608
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #F4D03F
skinparam ActivityDiamondFontColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityStartColor #2ECC71
skinparam ActivityEndColor #E74C3C
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam RoundCorner 10

title Three Execution Modes — System 1 / 2 / 3

|#2C3E50| Routing |
start

:<$microchip> **Task Arrives**
Receive structured ActionPlan from Deliberation Engine.
Load matching skill candidates from Procedural Memory.
Compute pattern-match confidence score;

if (confidence >= 0.90?) then (yes)
  :<color:#27AE60><$bolt></color> **System 1 — Fast Path**
  Direct pattern-matched execution.
  Pre-compiled tool call dispatched.
  No LLM inference needed.
  Latency: < 200ms;
elseif (confidence >= 0.50?) then (moderate)
  :<color:#2980B9><$brain></color> **System 2 — Deliberate**
  Step-by-step chain-of-thought reasoning.
  Claude API (Sonnet 4) generates action sequence.
  Tools called sequentially with validation.
  Latency: 5-30s;
else (low confidence)
  :<color:#E67E22><$cog></color> **System 3 — Tree Search (MCTS)**
  Generate N=5 candidate action trees.
  Simulate each path via State Predictor.
  Score by expected value and risk.
  Select optimal branch. Latency: 30-120s;
endif

:<$check_circle> **Execution Complete**
Dispatch selected action to Claude Code.
Monitor output stream for errors.
Capture final outcome and confidence;

|#2C3E50| Outcome |

if (Outcome matches expected?) then (success)
  :<$database> **Memory Update — Success**
  Persist success trace to Episodic store.
  Boost pattern weight in Procedural store.
  Increment autonomy score for this task class;
  stop
else (failure)
  :<$sync> **Memory Update — Failure**
  Log failure with context to Episodic store.
  Decrement pattern confidence.
  Flag for System 3 retry with extended budget;
  stop
endif
@enduml
